      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example benefits from a reinforced rear subframe and a recently overhauled VANOS system, ensuring structural integrity and variable valve timing precision. Power is delivered through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission to a factory variable M differential lock. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, providing the tactile feedback and high-speed stability characteristic of this chassis. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders and a smooth torque curve throughout the rev range.",
      "price": 34500.0,
